*   **[Empirical risk minimization](/Empirical_risk_minimization)**: Minimizing the error on the training data. A common optimization objective.
*   **[Occam learning](/Occam_learning)**: The principle that simpler explanations are generally better.
*   **[PAC learning](/Probably_approximately_correct_learning)**: A theoretical framework for analyzing learning algorithms.
*   **[Statistical learning theory](/Statistical_learning_theory)**: Applying statistical principles to machine learning.
*   **[VC theory](/Vapnik%E2%80%93Chervonenkis_theory)**: Vapnik–Chervonenkis theory. Analyzing the capacity of a hypothesis space.
